Type: Package
Package: vectorialcalculus
Title: Vector Calculus Tools for Visualization and Analysis in R
Version: 1.0.4
Authors@R: c(
    person("Julio", "Lizarazo Osorio", , "julio.lizarazo@uptc.edu.co", role = "aut",
           comment = c(affiliation = "Universidad Pedagógica y Tecnológica de Colombia (UPTC)")),
    person("Julian Mauricio", "Fajardo", , "julian.fajardo1908@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(affiliation = "Universidad El Bosque"))
  )
Description: Provides pedagogical functions for visualization and
    numerical computation in vector calculus. Includes tools for
    parametric curves, scalar and vector fields, gradients, divergences,
    curls, line and surface integrals, and 2D/3D dynamic plots to support
    teaching and analysis.
